The Armenian Academy of Sciences was founded by Joseph Orbeli in 1943 . One branch is based in Aragatsotn , Armenia and studies astronomy in the Byurakan Observatory . One of the founders and the first President of NAS RA was Full Member of the USSR and Armenian Academy of Sciences Prof. Hovsep Orbeli . During 1947 - 1993 the President of NAS RA was Prof. Victor Ambartsumian , Full Member of the USSR and Armenian Academies of Sciences . During 1993 - 2006 the President of NAS was Academician Fadey Sargsian . Since 2006 the President of NAS RA is Academician Radik Martirosyan . This European school - related article is a stub . 